quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  17,76,"Ne toto bali ahambi muno okhukhulonda kushialo (Madina) kho bakhurusiemwo. Ne shibakhekhale inyuma wuwo halali ebise bititi butswa."
  17,77,"Eyo niyo imelo ya balia abakhwaruma imbeli wuwo mubarumwa befu. Ne sholanyoola obwawukhani mu imelo yefu tawe."
  17,78,"Ne swaliya khatsotso eliuba niliakhakalukhana, okhula eshilima shieshilo, ne Ikurani yomumabwibwi. Toto Ikurani (Iswala) yomumabwibwi ili nende abaloli buli lwoosi."
  17,79,"Ne eshilo bukha olaame ninayo. Eyo ni eshimetelo khwiwe, yakhaba ario Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yakhulamusilia habundu woluyali."
  17,80,"Ne boola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, nyinjisia amenjililo amalayi, ne ndusia okhurusia okhulayi, ne umbe amaani karula khwiwe akakhonya.”"
  17,81,"Ne boola mbu: “Obwatoto buulile, ne obubeyi burulile. Toto obubeyi nibwo obwokhurulao muno.”"
  17,82,"Ne khweshia mu Kurani eshili mbu ni eshiwonia, nende tsimbabaasi khubasuubili, ne shishibametanga Abakhayi halali obusishi (okhutiba)."
  17,83,"Ne olwakhuwelesinjia Omundu tsimbabaasi tsiefu, akalukhananga mana yere elubeka. Ne libii nilimutila, afwitsanga omwoyo muno."
  17,84,"Boola mbu: “Buli shiamulala akholanga mu injila yiyie, ne Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi yamanya muno ulia owalunjikha muno injila.’’"
  17,85,"Ne bakhurebanga amakhuwa ka roho. Boola mbu: ‘‘Roho ni likhuwa lirulana nende Nyasaye wanje Omulesi. Nanyu shimwahebwa mubumanyi halali butiti.”"
  17,86,"Ne khwenyanga, toto khwakhabukule koosi aka khwakhufimbulila, mana shiwakhanyolele ukhwemela khwelo imbeli wefu tawe."